---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import BrandBranchesGrid from '../../components/BrandBranchesGrid.astro';
import { MAIN_PHONE, MAIN_PHONE_TEL } from '../../data/branches';

const title = "Fulgor Milano Stove Repair | Southern California | 600/700 Series + Sofia";
const description = "Fulgor Milano stove repair across Southern California, 600 Series, 700 Series, Sofia lines. Meneghetti S.p.A. Italian + Maple Distributing parts. $89 diagnostic. (424) 325-0520.";
const canonical = "https://samedayappliance.repair/brands/fulgor-milano-stove-repair/";

const faqs = [
  {
    q: "Who manufactures Fulgor Milano?",
    a: "Fulgor Milano is manufactured by <b>Meneghetti S.p.A.</b>, an Italian family-owned appliance manufacturer. Fulgor Milano is the brand's current residential luxury positioning; the Meneghetti corporate parent has been in Italian appliance manufacturing since the mid-20th century. For North American distribution, Fulgor Milano works through <b>Maple Distributing</b> which maintains US parts inventory with LA-region stock for common Fulgor service components. Italian-factory-source specialty parts typically 3-5 week lead; common service components 5-10 days through Maple Distributing. Distinct from other Italian family brands, Fulgor is Meneghetti, ILVE is a separate Treviso family, Smeg is Bermani / Guastalla, Bertazzoni is Guastalla / different family. No corporate overlap."
  },
  {
    q: "What Fulgor Milano stove lines are most common in LA?",
    a: "<b>600 Series</b> is the entry-luxury line, 30\" and 36\" freestanding with conventional controls + stainless or color trim; volume-line for Fulgor LA installs. <b>700 Series Pro</b> is the pro-style flagship, 30\"/36\"/48\" with heavier build, higher BTU burners, professional-grade construction, brass / stainless / color trim. <b>Sofia</b> is the vintage-inspired design line, rounded corners + brass detail aesthetic. LA Fulgor installs concentrate in design-forward mid-luxury kitchens, Santa Monica architectural remodels, Silver Lake design-district homes, Hancock Park heritage-adjacent kitchens, Pasadena established-luxury (not quite Bel Air / Beverly Hills ultra-luxury where Viking / Wolf / Thermador dominate). Fulgor typically sits a tier below Viking / BlueStar / ILVE in custom-kitchen spec but above mass-market premium."
  },
  {
    q: "Fulgor Milano burner not lighting, what's the fix?",
    a: "Standard Italian-pro-range diagnostic: (1) orifice verification on LP / NG mismatch; orifice $180–$260 per burner; (2) spark-module ignition $260–$380 at 7-10 year mark; (3) ignitor tip clean / replace $200–$300; (4) thermocouple flame-failure $200–$300 (EU safety-spec standard); (5) burner cap seating + port clean $160–$240 per burner; (6) gas valve partial restriction $280–$420; (7) regulator pressure $200–$300. Our techs carry Fulgor-specific igniters + thermocouples, Maple Distributing LA parts channel backfills common service components in 5-10 days typical."
  },
  {
    q: "Fulgor oven temperature inaccurate, diagnostic?",
    a: "Standard dual-fuel oven diagnostic: (1) sensor drift at 5-8 year mark; sensor $200–$300; (2) bake element (dual-fuel electric oven-side) $300–$440; (3) convection fan motor $320–$480; (4) control board $440–$640; (5) thermal fuse $220–$320; (6) door rope seal $180–$260. Fulgor oven-cavity dimensions run European-format on 700 Series, convection distribution pattern differs slightly from US-format pro-ranges; we verify temp at cavity corners during sensor calibration."
  },
  {
    q: "How does Fulgor Milano compare to ILVE or Bertazzoni?",
    a: "<b>Fulgor Milano (this page)</b>, Meneghetti Italian family, mid-luxury positioning, 600 + 700 + Sofia lines, 5-10 day parts through Maple Distributing LA channel. Volume in design-forward mid-luxury kitchens. <b>ILVE</b>, Treviso Italian family since 1975, broader luxury positioning (Majestic III flagship), 60+ colors + five knob-trim materials, 5-10 day parts through ILVE NA. See <a href='/brands/ilve-stove-repair/'>ILVE stove repair</a>. <b>Bertazzoni</b>, Guastalla Italian family since 1882, 6th generation heritage, Professional + Master + Heritage lines, 5-10 day parts through Bertazzoni USA. See <a href='/brands/bertazzoni-stove-repair/'>Bertazzoni stove repair</a>. Choice drivers: Fulgor for mid-luxury Italian value; ILVE for widest color + knob-trim flexibility; Bertazzoni for 6th-generation heritage + Professional Series pro-style."
  },
  {
    q: "Oven igniter glow-but-no-heat on Fulgor?",
    a: "Igniter resistance out-of-spec (glows but can't reach gas-valve trigger threshold), igniter swap $240–$360 on Fulgor pro-range oven-side. Related diagnostic: oven gas valve partial restriction $280–$420; safety thermocouple feedback $220–$320. Our techs carry Fulgor-specific igniters in LA dispatch."
  },
  {
    q: "Color-matched Fulgor panel replacement process?",
    a: "Fulgor color program runs through Meneghetti Italian factory. Replacement: (1) document exact color code from factory plate; (2) check Maple Distributing stock first; (3) if US-stocked color expect 3-5 weeks; (4) if Italian-factory-source expect 5-8 weeks. Panel prices quoted individually by color + model. Interior mechanical service runs independently on standard Fulgor pace during panel-sourcing wait."
  },
  {
    q: "What does Fulgor Milano stove repair cost in LA?",
    a: "Residential diagnostic $89 waived with repair. Typical Fulgor bands: orifice swap (per burner) $180–$260; spark-module $260–$380; ignitor tip $200–$300; thermocouple $200–$300; gas valve $280–$420; regulator $200–$300; oven igniter $240–$360; bake element $300–$440; convection fan motor $320–$480; temperature sensor $200–$300; control board $440–$640; door rope seal $180–$260; burner cap $140–$220. Color-matched panel quoted individually 3-8 week lead. Fulgor service economics run slightly below ILVE / Bertazzoni on individual parts reflecting mid-luxury positioning, 15-25% above mainstream-brand pricing."
  }
];

const schemaJsons = [
  { "@context": "https://schema.org", "@type": "LocalBusiness", "@id": canonical + "#business",
    "name": "Same Day Appliance Repair, Fulgor Milano Stove Service",
    "image": "https://samedayappliance.repair/images/same-day-appliance-repair.png",
    "url": canonical, "telephone": MAIN_PHONE_TEL, "priceRange": "$$$",
    "areaServed": [
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "Los Angeles County" },
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "Orange County" },
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "Ventura County" },
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "San Bernardino County" },
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "Riverside County" }
    ]
  },
  { "@context": "https://schema.org", "@type": "Service", "serviceType": "Fulgor Milano Stove Repair",
    "provider": { "@id": canonical + "#business" },
    "areaServed": [
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "Los Angeles County" },
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "Orange County" },
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "Ventura County" },
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "San Bernardino County" },
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "Riverside County" }
    ],
    "description": "Fulgor Milano stove repair across LA, 600 Series entry-luxury, 700 Series Pro flagship, Sofia vintage-inspired. Meneghetti S.p.A. Italian family manufacturer + Maple Distributing US parts network. $89 residential diagnostic waived with repair.",
    "offers": { "@type": "Offer", "priceSpecification": { "@type": "PriceSpecification", "price": "89.00", "priceCurrency": "USD", "description": "Residential diagnostic fee, waived with repair" } }
  },
  { "@context": "https://schema.org", "@type": "FAQPage", "mainEntity": faqs.map(f => ({ "@type": "Question", "name": f.q, "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": f.a } })) },
  { "@context": "https://schema.org", "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
    "itemListElement": [
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Home", "item": "https://samedayappliance.repair/" },
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "Brands", "item": "https://samedayappliance.repair/brands/" },
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 3, "name": "Fulgor Milano", "item": "https://samedayappliance.repair/brands/fulgor-milano/" },
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 4, "name": "Fulgor Milano Stove Repair", "item": canonical }
    ]
  }
];
---

<Layout title={title} description={description} canonical={canonical}>
  <Fragment slot="head-scripts">{schemaJsons.map((schema) => (<script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(schema)} />))}</Fragment>
  <div class="call-banner"><div class="wrap"><span>Fulgor Milano service? Same-day across LA:</span><a href={`tel:${MAIN_PHONE_TEL}`} class="phone-lg">{MAIN_PHONE}</a></div></div>

  <section class="hero"><div class="wrap">
    <div class="crumb"><a href="/">Home</a> › <a href="/brands/">Brands</a> › Fulgor Milano › Stove Repair</div>
    <h1>Fulgor Milano Stove Repair</h1>
    <p class="lede">Fulgor Milano is the Meneghetti S.p.A. Italian family-manufactured residential appliance brand, distributed in North America through Maple Distributing with LA-region parts stock for common service components. 600 Series entry-luxury, 700 Series Pro flagship, and Sofia vintage-inspired lines cover Fulgor's residential lineup. Fulgor sits at mid-luxury positioning in LA installed base, above mass-market premium, below Viking / BlueStar / ILVE in custom-kitchen spec concentration. Our service works through Maple Distributing parts channel with 5-10 day typical lead on common components, 3-5 weeks on Italian-factory-source specialty items. Concentrated installs in Santa Monica architectural remodels, Silver Lake design-district homes, Hancock Park heritage-adjacent kitchens, Pasadena established-luxury. Same-day dispatch, $89 residential diagnostic waived with the repair.</p>
    <div class="hero-cta"><a href={`tel:${MAIN_PHONE_TEL}`} class="btn btn-primary">Call {MAIN_PHONE}</a><a href="#book" class="btn btn-ghost">Request a Visit</a></div>
    <ul class="hero-facts">
      <li><b>Meneghetti S.p.A. Italian manufacturer</b>, family-owned</li>
      <li><b>Maple Distributing US parts</b>, LA-region stock, 5-10 day lead</li>
      <li><b>600 / 700 Pro / Sofia</b>, mid-luxury through flagship pro-style</li>
      <li><b>$89 residential diagnostic</b>, waived when you authorize the repair</li>
    </ul>
  </div></section>

  <BrandBranchesGrid />

  <section class="trust-bar"><div class="wrap"><span>BHGS #A49573 · Insured</span><span>Same-day in 5 SoCal counties</span><span>Residential diagnostic $89 · waived with repair</span></div></section>

  <section class="section"><div class="wrap narrow">
    <h2>Fulgor Milano in LA, mid-luxury Italian family manufacturing</h2>
    <p>Fulgor Milano occupies a specific LA market position: Italian family-manufactured residential appliance with mid-luxury positioning, volume in design-forward mid-luxury kitchens where ILVE / Bertazzoni / BlueStar are a tier-higher spec. Meneghetti S.p.A. manufactures in Italy with established parts distribution through Maple Distributing's US network, LA-region parts availability is the practical service advantage for common components (igniters, thermocouples, sensors, burner caps) with 5-10 day typical lead vs 2-4 weeks on brands that require direct Italian factory sourcing for every part.</p>
    <p>LA Fulgor installs concentrate where Italian-family manufacturing + mid-luxury value is specifically valued. Santa Monica architectural remodels; Silver Lake + Los Feliz design-district homes; Hancock Park heritage-adjacent kitchens (not the ultra-luxury tier where Bertazzoni Heritage Series dominates, but the tier below); Pasadena + San Marino established-luxury installs; Manhattan Beach coastal-modern kitchens. Service approach respects Italian-spec engineering, we verify EU-spec thermocouple flame-failure devices, European-format oven-cavity dimensions, and color-matched finish integrity on any exterior-adjacent work.</p>
  </div></section>

  <section class="section alt"><div class="wrap">
    <h2>Fulgor Milano stove failures our techs see most often in LA</h2>
    <div class="fail-block"><h3>Gas burner no-light, orifice / spark / thermocouple</h3><p>Most common service. Orifice $180–$260 per burner; spark module $260–$380; thermocouple $200–$300.</p></div>
    <div class="fail-block"><h3>Oven temperature drift</h3><p>Sensor drift at 5-8 years. Sensor $200–$300; control board $440–$640.</p></div>
    <div class="fail-block"><h3>Convection fan motor</h3><p>Motor swap $320–$480 on dual-fuel 700 Series.</p></div>
    <div class="fail-block"><h3>Oven igniter glow-but-no-heat</h3><p>Igniter $240–$360 on Fulgor pro-range oven-side.</p></div>
    <div class="fail-block"><h3>Oven door rope seal</h3><p>10+ year degradation. Seal swap $180–$260 per door.</p></div>
    <div class="fail-block"><h3>Color-matched panel service</h3><p>Meneghetti Italian factory sourcing. 3-8 week lead through Maple Distributing.</p></div>
  </div></section>

  <section class="section"><div class="wrap">
    <h2>Fulgor Milano product lines we service</h2>
    <div class="model-grid">
      <div class="model-card"><h3>600 Series (entry-luxury)</h3><p>30"/36" freestanding. Conventional controls. Stainless + color trim. Volume-line LA.</p></div>
      <div class="model-card"><h3>700 Series Pro (flagship)</h3><p>30"/36"/48" pro-style. Heavier build + higher BTU burners. Brass / stainless / color trim.</p></div>
      <div class="model-card"><h3>Sofia (vintage-inspired)</h3><p>Rounded-corner styling. Brass detail. Traditional-design kitchens.</p></div>
      <div class="model-card"><h3>Dual-fuel configurations</h3><p>Gas cooktop + electric convection oven on 700 Pro. Standard luxury format.</p></div>
      <div class="model-card"><h3>Color program</h3><p>Meneghetti factory-matched colors. Limited vs ILVE / BlueStar scale but curated.</p></div>
      <div class="model-card"><h3>Maple Distributing parts channel</h3><p>US parts stock + LA-region availability. 5-10 day typical lead.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div></section>

  <section class="section alt"><div class="wrap narrow">
    <h2>Fulgor Milano vs ILVE vs Bertazzoni, Italian family tiers</h2>
    <p>Three Italian family-manufactured residential brands at different luxury-tier positions.</p>
    <p><b>Fulgor Milano (this page)</b>, Meneghetti family, mid-luxury positioning, 600 + 700 + Sofia, Maple Distributing US parts with LA-region stock.</p>
    <p><b>ILVE</b>, Treviso family since 1975, broader luxury (Majestic III flagship + Nostalgie II + Panoramagic), 60+ colors, five knob-trim materials. See <a href="/brands/ilve-stove-repair/">ILVE stove repair</a>.</p>
    <p><b>Bertazzoni</b>, Guastalla family since 1882, 6th generation, Professional + Master + Heritage lines, 60+ enamel colors. See <a href="/brands/bertazzoni-stove-repair/">Bertazzoni stove repair</a>.</p>
    <p>Choice drivers: Fulgor for mid-luxury Italian value + Maple Distributing LA-region parts; ILVE for widest flexibility; Bertazzoni for longest family heritage.</p>
  </div></section>

  <section class="section"><div class="wrap">
    <h2>What Fulgor Milano stove repair costs in LA</h2>
    <table class="price-table">
      <tr><th>Service</th><th>Typical Range</th><th>Notes</th></tr>
      <tr><td>Residential diagnostic</td><td>$89</td><td>Waived with repair</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Orifice swap (per burner)</td><td>$180 – $260</td><td>LP / NG mismatch</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Burner cap replacement</td><td>$140 – $220</td><td>Per burner</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Spark-module ignition</td><td>$260 – $380</td><td>7-10 year service</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Ignitor tip clean / replace</td><td>$200 – $300</td><td>Carbon / electrode wear</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Thermocouple flame-failure</td><td>$200 – $300</td><td>EU safety spec</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Gas-line regulator</td><td>$200 – $300</td><td>Pressure stability</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Gas valve swap</td><td>$280 – $420</td><td>Stuck / restricted</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Oven igniter</td><td>$240 – $360</td><td>Pro-range oven-side</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Bake element (dual-fuel)</td><td>$300 – $440</td><td>Electric oven-side</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Convection fan motor</td><td>$320 – $480</td><td>Dual-fuel dependency</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Temperature sensor</td><td>$200 – $300</td><td>Oven accuracy</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Thermal fuse / high-limit</td><td>$220 – $320</td><td>Safety cutout</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Oven door rope seal</td><td>$180 – $260</td><td>Per door</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Control board</td><td>$440 – $640</td><td>Digital control logic</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Color-matched panel</td><td>Quoted individually</td><td>3-8 week lead</td></tr>
    </table>
    <p class="small">Related: <a href="/brands/fulgor-milano/">Fulgor Milano brand hub</a> · <a href="/brands/ilve-stove-repair/">ILVE stove repair</a> · <a href="/brands/bertazzoni-stove-repair/">Bertazzoni stove repair</a>.</p>
  </div></section>

  <section class="section alt"><div class="wrap">
    <h2>LA service areas, where our Fulgor Milano stove calls come from</h2>
    <div class="area-grid">
      <div><h4>Santa Monica + Venice</h4><p>Santa Monica · Venice · Mar Vista</p></div>
      <div><h4>Silver Lake + Los Feliz</h4><p>Silver Lake · Los Feliz · Echo Park</p></div>
      <div><h4>Hancock Park</h4><p>Hancock Park · Larchmont · Windsor Square</p></div>
      <div><h4>Pasadena + San Marino</h4><p><a href="/pasadena/">Pasadena</a> · San Marino · La Cañada</p></div>
      <div><h4>Manhattan Beach</h4><p>Manhattan Beach · Hermosa · Redondo Beach</p></div>
      <div><h4>OC mid-luxury</h4><p>Newport Beach · Costa Mesa · <a href="/irvine/">Irvine</a></p></div>
    </div>
  </div></section>

  <section class="section"><div class="wrap narrow">
    <h2>Related Fulgor Milano and Italian-family pages</h2>
    <ul class="related-links">
      <li><a href="/brands/fulgor-milano/">Fulgor Milano brand hub →</a></li>
      <li><a href="/brands/ilve-stove-repair/">ILVE stove repair →</a></li>
      <li><a href="/brands/bertazzoni-stove-repair/">Bertazzoni stove repair →</a></li>
      <li><a href="/brands/smeg-stove-repair/">Smeg stove repair →</a></li>
      <li><a href="/services/stove-repair/">Stove repair (service hub) →</a></li>
      <li><a href="/price-list/stove-repair-cost/">Stove repair cost guide →</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div></section>

  <section class="section alt"><div class="wrap narrow">
    <h2>Fulgor Milano stove repair, frequently asked</h2>
    {faqs.map(f => (<details class="faq"><summary>{f.q}</summary><p set:html={f.a}></p></details>))}
  </div></section>

  <section id="book" class="cta-bottom"><div class="wrap">
    <h2>Fulgor Milano service? Call the branch closest to your home.</h2>
    <p>Same-day appliance repair in Los Angeles, Orange County, Ventura County. Residential diagnostic $89, waived with repair.</p>
  </div></section>
  <a href={`tel:${MAIN_PHONE_TEL}`} class="float-call" aria-label="Call now">☎ Call {MAIN_PHONE}</a>
</Layout>

<style>
  :root { --red: #C8102E; --black: #0a0a0a; --gray: #f5f5f5; --border: #e2e2e2; --text: #1a1a1a; --muted: #6b6b6b; }
  body { color: var(--text); } .wrap { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 24px; } .wrap.narrow { max-width: 820px; }
  h1 { font-size: 2.4rem; line-height: 1.15; margin: 12px 0 20px; color: var(--black); }
  h2 { font-size: 1.8rem; margin: 0 0 16px; color: var(--black); }
  h3 { font-size: 1.2rem; margin: 0 0 10px; color: var(--black); }
  h4 { font-size: 1.02rem; margin: 0 0 6px; color: var(--black); }
  p { line-height: 1.65; margin: 0 0 14px; }
  .call-banner { background: var(--red); color: #fff; padding: 10px 0; }
  .call-banner .wrap { display:flex; gap: 14px; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .call-banner .phone-lg { color:#fff; font-weight: 800; text-decoration: underline; font-size: 1.05rem; }
  .hero { background: var(--black); color: #fff; padding: 42px 0 56px; } .hero h1 { color: #fff; }
  .hero .lede { font-size: 1.06rem; color: #d7d7d7; max-width: 680px; }
  .hero .crumb { color: #9a9a9a; font-size: 0.85rem; margin-bottom: 6px; } .hero .crumb a { color: #c9c9c9; text-decoration: none; }
  .hero-cta { display: flex; gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin: 18px 0 24px; }
  .btn { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 20px; border-radius: 4px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 700; }
  .btn-primary { background: var(--red); color: #fff; } .btn-ghost { background: transparent; color: #fff; border: 1px solid #fff; }
  .hero-facts { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; color: #c9c9c9; font-size: 0.95rem; }
  .hero-facts li { padding: 6px 0; border-top: 1px solid #222; } .hero-facts li:first-child { border-top: 0; }
  .trust-bar { background: var(--red); color: #fff; padding: 14px 0; }
  .trust-bar .wrap { display: flex; gap: 28px; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 600; }
  .section { padding: 56px 0; } .section.alt { background: var(--gray); }
  .model-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr)); gap: 20px; margin-top: 24px; }
  .model-card { background: #fff; border: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 20px; border-radius: 6px; }
  .section.alt .model-card { background: #fff; }
  .fail-block { background: #fff; border-left: 3px solid var(--red); padding: 20px 22px; margin: 16px 0; }
  .price-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-top: 14px; background: #fff; }
  .price-table th, .price-table td { text-align: left; padding: 11px 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .price-table th { background: var(--black); color: #fff; font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.95rem; }
  .small { color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.92rem; margin-top: 12px; }
  .area-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr)); gap: 18px; }
  .area-grid > div { background: #fff; border: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 16px; border-radius: 6px; }
  .related-links { list-style: none; padding: 0; } .related-links li { padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .related-links a { color: var(--red); font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; } .related-links a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
  .faq { background: #fff; border: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 12px 16px; margin-bottom: 8px; border-radius: 4px; }
  .faq summary { font-weight: 700; cursor: pointer; padding: 4px 0; } .faq p { margin: 8px 0 0; }
  .cta-bottom { background: var(--black); color: #fff; padding: 48px 0; } .cta-bottom h2 { color: #fff; } .cta-bottom p { color: #c9c9c9; }
  .float-call { position: fixed; bottom: 18px; right: 18px; background: var(--red); color: #fff; padding: 14px 18px; border-radius: 40px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 700; box-shadow: 0 6px 18px rgba(0,0,0,0.28); z-index: 50; font-size: 0.95rem; }
  @media (max-width: 820px) { h1 { font-size: 1.9rem; } h2 { font-size: 1.45rem; } .float-call { padding: 11px 14px; font-size: 0.88rem; } .trust-bar .wrap { gap: 14px; font-size: 0.85rem; } }
</style>
